metadata.description: 3rd in series. As usual, the Doctor has many adventures while helping his animal friends and the people he meets. At the start book, Doctor Dolittle gets help from the sea birds to help to capture a notorious slave trader and free his captives, then organizes the postal service of a small African kingdom. This grows into a worldwide postal & publishing service for the benefit of animals everywhere. (shortened summary, Phil Chenevert, LibriVox v.1)
